"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"存储期决定生命周期："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 变量的存储期（自动、静态、动态）决定了其在程序运行期间的生命周期。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-sbyl938","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-sbyl938","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-o52nct8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-o52nct8","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"栈空间具有临时性："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 栈上的变量在函数调用时分配，函数返回时释放，具有快速分配和回收的特点。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-gk6hxtx","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gk6hxtx","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-kug7lcr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-kug7lcr","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"数据段/BSS 段空间持久性："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 存储在数据段和 BSS 段的变量具有静态存储期，贯穿整个程序的生命周期，其值在函数调用结束后依然保留。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-dnva7iy","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-dnva7iy","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-vhmvljx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vhmvljx","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"堆空间手动管理："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 堆上的内存由程序员手动分配和释放，提供了最大的灵活性，但也带来了内存泄漏和碎片化的风险。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-tnf804f","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"5.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":5,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-tnf804f","updated":"20260305082130"},"Childre